divs: Sighting DetailsI was out in my yard when a strange feeling came over me as if I was being watched. I then went in the house and got my camera and just started taking photos of the sky. I could see or hear anything but their was that feeling that I had. Later on I was looking at my pics when I notice this thing in the clouds.
Summary: A dark solid planet looking object reddish brown color.
